===== 2026-06-05T14:10:29.027309 GTaskSheet-80mo.8 model=sonnet =====
**Root cause:** `open_sidebar(addon_name="GActionSheet")` had the wrong default. The actual add-on name in `appsscript.json` is `"Northlake Doc Tools"` — so `[aria-label*="GActionSheet"]` never matched, causing a 45s timeout. This was masked in `test_journey.py` because Act 3b has a D4 `try/except` guard.

**Fix:** `scn/ui.py` now derives `_ADDON_NAME` from `appsscript.json` at module load (same pattern as `addon_helpers.js`) and uses it as the `open_sidebar` default. 198 unit tests pass; the browser tests require live deployment to confirm green.

